statements: SELECT * FROM ProductionMetrics;
SELECT id, object_name, success_rate FROM ProductionMetrics ORDER BY success_rate DESC;
SELECT id, object_name, printing_time_minutes FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE material_type = 'PLA';
SELECT object_name, success_rate FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE printing_time_minutes > 60;
SELECT * FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE success_rate >= 90 AND material_type = 'ABS';
SELECT * FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE success_rate >= 90 ORDER BY printing_time_minutes DESC;
SELECT object_name, COUNT(*) AS total_count FROM ProductionMetrics GROUP BY object_name HAVING total_count > 2;
SELECT id, object_name, success_rate FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE material_type = 'PLA' OR material_type = 'ABS';
SELECT object_name, AVG(success_rate) AS average_success_rate FROM ProductionMetrics GROUP BY object_name ORDER BY average_success_rate DESC;
SELECT object_name, material_type, success_rate FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE success_rate < 80 AND material_type <> 'PETG';
SELECT * FROM ProductionMetrics
SELECT object_id, object_name, production_date FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE material_used = 'PLA'
SELECT printer_name, manufacturer FROM 3DPrinters ORDER BY manufacturer ASC
SELECT * FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE print_time_hours > 10
SELECT object_name, production_date, print_time_hours FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE production_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31' ORDER BY production_date DESC
SELECT * FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE production_date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT object_name, material_used FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE print_time_hours > 5;
SELECT * FROM 3DPrinters WHERE manufacturer = 'XYZ Corp';
SELECT printer_name, manufacturer, build_volume FROM 3DPrinters WHERE printer_id IN (1, 3);
SELECT object_name, material_used, print_time_hours FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE material_used LIKE '%PLA%' ORDER BY object_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM 3d_printer_metrics;
SELECT object_name, material_used FROM 3d_printer_metrics WHERE print_volume > 100;
SELECT id, printer_model, warranty_end_date FROM printer_inventory ORDER BY printer_location DESC;
SELECT * FROM print_history WHERE success = true;
SELECT object_name, object_type, print_volume FROM 3d_printer_metrics WHERE material_used='PLA'
SELECT * FROM 3d_printer_metrics WHERE print_volume > 100 ORDER BY print_time DESC;
SELECT object_name, material_used FROM 3d_printer_metrics WHERE object_type = 'Figurine' AND print_time > '1 day';
SELECT printer_model, printer_location FROM printer_inventory WHERE purchase_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' ORDER BY purchase_date;
SELECT * FROM print_history WHERE success = true AND failure_reason IS NULL ORDER BY print_date DESC;
SELECT p.printer_model, COUNT(ph.id) AS print_count FROM printer_inventory p JOIN print_history ph ON p.id = ph.printer_id GROUP BY p.printer_model HAVING print_count > 5 ORDER BY print_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM ProductionMetrics;
SELECT object_name, print_time, filament_weight FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE success = true;
SELECT model_id, manufacturer FROM PrinterModels ORDER BY manufacturer;
SELECT * FROM MaterialTypes WHERE material_cost > 50.00;
SELECT object_size, infill_density FROM ObjectProperties WHERE layer_height = 0.2;
SELECT object_name, filament_weight FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE success = true;
SELECT model_id, manufacturer FROM PrinterModels ORDER BY manufacturer DESC;
SELECT material_name, material_density, material_cost FROM MaterialTypes WHERE material_cost < 100 ORDER BY material_density DESC;
SELECT object_id, object_size, layer_height FROM ObjectProperties WHERE infill_density > 0.5 ORDER BY object_size ASC;
SELECT * FROM ProductionMetrics pm JOIN ObjectProperties op ON pm.id = op.object_id WHERE op.layer_height < 0.2 AND pm.filament_weight > 200;
SELECT * FROM ProductionMetrics
SELECT object_name, quantity FROM ProductionMetrics ORDER BY quantity DESC
SELECT printer_id, failure_count FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE failure_count > 0
SELECT * FROM Printer WHERE manufacturer = 'HP'
SELECT operator_name, experience_years FROM PrintOperator
SELECT * FROM ProductionMetrics WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY object_name DESC
SELECT printer_name, manufacturer FROM Printer WHERE location = 'Warehouse'
SELECT pm.object_name, pm.quantity, p.printer_name FROM ProductionMetrics pm JOIN Printer p ON pm.printer_id = p.id WHERE pm.failure_count > 10
SELECT material_name, cost_per_kg FROM PrintMaterial WHERE material_type = 'ABS' ORDER BY cost_per_kg ASC
SELECT po.operator_name, po.experience_years FROM PrintOperator po WHERE po.operator_type = 'Senior'
